{
  "text": "As shown in Fig. 1A , netoglitazone was approximately two orders of magnitude less effective than rosiglitazone in inducing adipocyte differentiation in U-33/\u03b32 cells. This finding is consistent with previous reports demonstrating that netoglitazone was approximately 10 times less effective in inducing adipogenesis in 3T3-L1 cells [CITATION_1] .",
